value:
When Dagr was young, she broke
many a training dummy... I hear she
may not be alone in that here, hm?

Mother is a great queen. But when
she gets angry, it can be frightening...
like she will tear the land itself apart.

There is no harm in being friendly
with Dagr...so long as you are careful
not to adopt her crude mannerisms.

Oh, but you do look fatigued... Would
you care to eat something? I do know
something of proper nutrition.

When I visit other lands, my size often
calls attention to me. Here, however,
it is hardly the most unusual sight.

I am here to offer a greeting by the
grace of $Nf...

I strive toward perfection. Continued
improvement is expected of me.

Not awful, I suppose...though I ought
to remain positive.
Urgh... What an embarrassment...

That's one step closer to becoming
queen... You have my gratitude.

I am Nótt, Jötunheimr's next queen.
I hope we can forge friendly relations
between our two grand realms.

Dagr and I have not always quarreled
as we do now. We were once quite
close, in fact...$k$pBut we were born princesses of
Jötunheimr, so we could not remain
on friendly terms forever.$k$pOne of us must one day be queen.
That means we must make certain
sacrifices...for the realm.$k$pWhen we were children, I never lost
to Dagr, but she's grown into an
entirely different jötun...$k$pNow, if I do not take her seriously,
she can easily outmatch me during
a fight...$k$pI believe I have you to thank you for
that, $Nu...$k$pAs her older sister, thank you.$k$pHowever! I will NOT lose to her, so
I must learn all I can while I am here
in this realm! Now, what's next...
はあっ
Concede
ああっ…
How unkind...
Just die.
Shameful!
Scrawny little runt!
You offend me.
I lost...
Uhuhu...
I am the firstborn princess of Jötunheimr, Nótt. I do hope we can get along.
Oh! A touch is a fair greeting.
I will be the one to succeed my honored mother, as Jötunheimr's next queen.
Dagr is so unrefined...it's perfectly indecent! How can she be my sister?
Excuse me...Summoner? I hear that a tight embrace is a symbol of great affection with your people. Is that true?
The Order has brought together so many beauteous Heroes... My eyes may become exhausted by their radiance!
My body and mind are already yours... I pledge myself to your cause.
As you command.
Quite a challenge!
It's over for them.
